Package cs321.superscrabble

Class Summary
SBoard This class is responsible for tracking tile positions on the board.
SBoardSwing This class oversees display of the Scrabble board.
Scrabble This class oversees implementation of various Scrabble rules.
ScrabbleFrame This class oversees initialization and placement of all GUI components.
ScrabbleListener This class oversees the functionality of the GUI buttons.
SPieces This class oversees tile distribution, and takes care of producing fresh tiles for the rack.
SRack This class oversees tracking of currently racked tiles.
SuperScrabble This class oversees execution of SuperScrabble.
